# 3. Correct solving strategy

There are **only three possible unknowns**.

### Case 1 — carrier unknown

[
\omega_c =
\frac{N_s\omega_s + N_r\omega_r}{N_s + N_r}
]

---

### Case 2 — sun unknown

[
\omega_s =
\frac{(N_s + N_r)\omega_c - N_r\omega_r}{N_s}
]

---

### Case 3 — ring unknown

[
\omega_r =
\frac{(N_s + N_r)\omega_c - N_s\omega_s}{N_r}
]

